<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Skill-Swapz - Learn</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.6/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #2c5364 80%);
            color: #fff;
        }
        .learn-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31,38,135,0.37);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
            padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
            margin-top: 3rem;
        }
        .learn-card h1 {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .btn-custom {
            background: #ffd700;
            color: #222;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: none;
        }
        .btn-custom:hover {
            background: #fff;
            color: #222;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center" style="min-height:100vh;">
        <div class="learn-card text-center">
            <h1>Welcome to the Learn Page!</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-4">
                Here you can ask questions, answer others, and upvote the best solutions.<br>
                Join the community and start sharing your knowledge!
            </p>
            <a href="/questions" class="btn btn-custom btn-lg mb-2">Go to Q&amp;A</a><br>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-light">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
